IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. REPORTER.
ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
FILE-CONTROL.
    SELECT IN-FILE ASSIGN TO "/tmp/employees.dat"
        ORGANIZATION IS SEQUENTIAL.
    SELECT OUT-FILE ASSIGN TO "/tmp/report.dat"
        ORGANIZATION IS SEQUENTIAL.
DATA DIVISION.
FILE SECTION.
FD IN-FILE.
01 EMP-REC.
    05 EMP-NAME PIC X(20).
    05 EMP-SAL PIC 9(7)V99.
FD OUT-FILE.
01 OUT-REC.
    05 OUT-NAME PIC X(20).
    05 OUT-SAL PIC 9(7)V99.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 EOF-FLAG PIC X VALUE "N".
    88 EOF-REACHED VALUE "Y".
01 TOTAL PIC 9(9)V99 VALUE 0.
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MAIN-PROC.
    OPEN INPUT IN-FILE.
    OPEN OUTPUT OUT-FILE.
    READ IN-FILE AT END MOVE "Y" TO EOF-FLAG END-READ.
    PERFORM UNTIL EOF-REACHED
        MOVE EMP-NAME TO OUT-NAME
        MOVE EMP-SAL TO OUT-SAL
        WRITE OUT-REC
        ADD EMP-SAL TO TOTAL
        READ IN-FILE AT END MOVE "Y" TO EOF-FLAG END-READ
    END-PERFORM.
    CLOSE IN-FILE.
    CLOSE OUT-FILE.
    DISPLAY TOTAL.
    STOP RUN.
